acho que isso é tudo

ENGLISH >>
01/17/26, Today I finish the first version of the game activity, however, there are some bugs in the racing game, as reaching 50 ~ 55
points the game bugs and loses automatically, I will try to solve this in future versions but it's quite difficult now.       

The game has only 3 buttons, start, left and right, up and down were disabled

the game has the blue car, the player who dodges from left to right
the red car, which moves at a normal speed
and the yellow car which is 1.2x faster than the red car

the snake game is bugged for some reason I couldn't find out, but I think it must have been some css that I accidentally changed

I put some random images for the cars, I thought it was cool, I even tried to remove the white background but I think vs code does not recognize
that the image is backgroundless and it stays black.
In addition, for each point made the game speeds up by 1.050x, making it more difficult to dodge the cars :>
the base of the game, besides the snake game was made by my web programming teacher, but I don't know how to give the due credits
sorry for that professor if you are reading this :<

I had help from some youtube channels to learn the logic of js, but I don't remember which ones, if I remember I put it here when I return to the code

I think that's all




